    "description": "Fukuvi Chemical Industry Co.,Ltd. engages in manufacturing, processing, and sale of synthetic resin products and inorganic compounds in Japan and internationally. The company operates through Construction Materials, CSE Business, Precision Business, Global Business, and Other segments. It manufactures and sells plastic extrusion of construction and industrial products under the Fukuvi brands. The company also provides skirting boards, wood plastic composite products, ceilings, multi-layer flooring products, inspection opening frames, plastic transitions, and rustication strips, as well as corner beads for walls. In addition, the company engages in development, manufacture, and sale of exterior and interior building materials, floor-related materials, system building materials, etc. Further, it manufactures phenolic foam insulation board and provides management services. It serves original equipment manufacturer. Fukuvi Chemical Industry Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1947 and is headquartered in Fukui, Japan."
